{"tid":2109011,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"經典大進化　神人以 UE4 重製《GTA：聖安地列斯》","createTime":"2020-07-15T02:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T08:59:11.000Z","uid":1121,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6d8555cb4d259aa4106247012b82eff00fc4d7b1","tid":2109011,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T02:40:17.000Z","msg":"雖然每一代的 GTA 品質總是能讓玩家信服，但《GTA：聖安地列斯》仍然是系列作粉絲心目中難以取代的經典。而現在有 3 名粉絲組成的小組，透過 4 年的時間建立了他們「以 UE4 打造《GTA：聖安地列斯》」的計畫，並且在最近釋出了預告影像，在網路上引發熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/GTA-SA-UE4-1536x804.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2FGTA-SA-UE4-1536x804.jpg&h=3a1f0443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你可以從下方影片中看到 UE4 版本《GTA：聖安地列斯》的預告，該預告可說是彌補了玩家渴望 Rockstar Games 重製該作品的缺憾。先前他們曾苦於缺少完整的地圖，使該計畫面臨瓶頸，但現在他們終於重建了整個《GTA：聖安地列斯》的世界，並且透過預告的方式向其它玩家們分享他們的成果。<br />\n<br />\nUE4 版《GTA：聖安地列斯》預告<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hPEKOlFO88o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhPEKOlFO88o&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu0BBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=657e0359\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hPEKOlFO88o</a>"},{"pid":"0d56afa24a00895d2b2398925f95a0f114ddde4e","tid":2109011,"uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T02:40:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/07/14/gta-聖安地列斯-ue4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2020%2F07%2F14%2Fgta-%E8%81%96%E5%AE%89%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%97%E6%96%AF-ue4%2F&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu0BBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=509e58cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/07/14/gta-聖安地列斯-ue4/</a>"},{"pid":"54cd32c8cf4a31230e4c91875ade193c84289a16","tid":2109011,"uid":52939,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T03:55:16.000Z","msg":"三個人咁撚DIN?"},{"pid":"69604a1d11172e72b3e6ea22